---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base
  title="Privacy Policy | Atherton & Co"
  description="Privacy Policy for Atherton & Co accounting services."
>
  <section class="py-16 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
    <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-8">Privacy Policy</h1>
    
    <!-- PLACEHOLDER: Review and customize this privacy policy for your business -->
    <div class="prose prose-lg text-gray-700 space-y-6">
      <p class="text-sm text-amber-700 bg-amber-50 border border-amber-200 rounded-lg p-4">
        <strong>Note:</strong> This is placeholder content. Please review and update this privacy policy to reflect your actual data practices and comply with applicable laws.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8">Information We Collect</h2>
      <p>
        We collect information you provide directly to us, such as when you contact us, 
        request our services, or communicate with us via email or phone.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8">How We Use Your Information</h2>
      <p>
        We use the information we collect to provide, maintain, and improve our accounting 
        and financial services, to communicate with you, and to comply with legal obligations.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8">Information Sharing</h2>
      <p>
        We do not sell or rent your personal information to third parties. We may share 
        information with service providers who assist us in operating our business, or 
        when required by law.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8">Data Security</h2>
      <p>
        We implement appropriate security measures to protect your personal information 
        against unauthorized access, alteration, disclosure, or destruction.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8">Contact Us</h2>
      <p>
        If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at the 
        information provided on our website.
      </p>

      <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mt-8">
        Last updated: [Insert Date]
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>
